# Global Social Experiment (Georgetown) — Podcast Artifact (NU Transcript)

This repository is a citable evidence package documenting where the phrase **“global social experiment”** is explicitly used to describe a project underway at **Georgetown University**, as stated in the transcript of a National University podcast episode.

